TO THE REUNION

09:15.800 --> 09:16.834
AS A BELOVED TEACHER,

09:16.834 --> 09:18.700
NOT UNLIKE
YOURSELF, SIR.

09:18.700 --> 09:21.100
OH, HOW FLATTERING.

09:21.100 --> 09:23.967
