IN MY FOOTSTEPS,

09:23.967 --> 09:26.967
AND, LOOK, YOU'VE
DRESSED JUST LIKE ME.

09:26.967 --> 09:30.834
COME OVER HERE,
YOU LITTLE SUCK UP.

09:30.834 --> 09:34.667
EVERY YEAR SOMEONE TRIES
TO AVOID THE ASSIGNMENT

09:34.667 --> 09:37.100
WITH THIS TRANSPARENT
LITTLE RUSE.

09:37.100 --> 09:38.400
