TO BE RUSE.

09:38.400 --> 09:40.734
CAN YOU TELL ME THE MEANING
OF THE WORD "TENURE"?

09:40.734 --> 09:41.767
I CAN LOOK IT UP.

09:41.767 --> 09:43.734
CAN YOU DEFINE
CURRICULUM?

09:43.734 --> 09:44.734
I CAN LOOK IT UP.

09:44.734 --> 09:47.400
