SEEM TO THINK SO.

10:07.000 --> 10:09.400
THEN YOU'RE QUITE
WELL-KNOWN?

10:09.400 --> 10:13.367
BREAKFAST OF ME.

10:13.367 --> 10:16.033
HOW'S IT FEEL TO BE IN
THE PRESENCE OF A LEGEND?

10:16.033 --> 10:18.500
