10:20.367 --> 10:22.300
OH, EVER SINCE
THE 11th GRADE.

10:22.300 --> 10:24.367
YOU DIDN'T GRADUATE
HIGH SCHOOL?

10:24.367 --> 10:26.133
HIGH SCHOOL'S
KIND OF A JOKE

10:26.133 --> 10:28.734
WHEN YOU'RE PULLING DOWN
6 MIL A YEAR.

10:28.734 --> 10:29.900
6 MILLION?

10:29.900 --> 10:31.667
HURTS, DOESN'T IT?

10:31.667 --> 10:33.967
WELL, ADJUSTED
FOR INFLATION,

10:33.967 --> 10:36.033
THAT'S A PALTRY SUM
COMPARED TO EVEN

10:36.033 --> 10:39.600
THE AVERAGE BALLPLAYER'S
SALARY TODAY.

10:39.600 --> 10:42.967
BUT I'VE GOT
INVESTMENTS.

10:42.967 --> 10:43.967
SUCH AS?

10:43.967 --> 10:46.100
YOU KNOW,
INVESTMENTS, UH...

10:46.100 --> 10:49.200
BUILDINGS.
BUILDINGS WITH FLOORS

10:49.200 --> 10:50.767
AND PEOPLE IN THEM
DOING STUFF.

10:50.767 --> 10:51.867
I'M DIVERSIFIED.

10:51.867 --> 10:54.300
AND DO YOU HANDLE THESE
INVESTMENTS YOURSELF?

10:54.300 --> 10:56.000
NO. MY GUYS
DO THAT STUFF.

10:56.000 --> 10:57.667
OH, YOU'VE GOT GUYS?

10:57.667 --> 11:00.734
LOTS OF GUYS.
THEY'RE IN MY BUILDINGS.

11:00.734 --> 11:02.800
