DAYS ARE OVER.

11:26.967 --> 11:29.000
BUT I'VE GOT GUYS.

11:29.000 --> 11:30.500
WELL, MR. MATTHEWS,

11:30.500 --> 11:32.734
YOU'VE MADE AN ATTEMPT
AT THIS ASSIGNMENT.

11:32.734 --> 11:34.500
